snippet.title: Let's Play Yu-Gi-Oh 5D's Decade Duels Plus - Episode 1
snippet.description:
I decided to try out something new and play the newly released Yu-Gi-Oh 5D's game on the Playstation 3 with commentary! Let me know what you all think of this different type of video. If it's well-received, I'll upload more episodes!

In This Episode:
Fortune Cup Preliminaries - Round 1

Help me to reach 1,000 Subscribers!

Give this video a Thumbs Up! Then Favorite it! Then leave a Comment! And maybe even Share it with your friends!

IMPORTANT LINKS!!

Read my blog!
http://teamaps.blogspot.com/

Join me on ustream for occassional experimental live streaming!
http://www.ustream.tv/channel/team-aps-live-yu-gi-oh-streaming

Contact me via PM or through my email address:
officialteamaps@gmail.com

Check out my Channel for even more Yu-Gi-Oh TCG Content!
http://www.youtube.com/user/TeamAPS

I'm a Yu-Gi-Oh Judge and videographer. I record videos at home and every week at my local card shop. Everything is in high-definition, and I try to put out a video every day. I am always open to suggestions for improvements and new video segments. I also openly accept Channel features. Let me know if you want one of your videos featured! Find me on Facebook!
https://www.facebook.com/teamapsyt
